_sText:
Put in C:\Program Files\Steam\steamaps\<username>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
This is a remake of hosties_WhiteCastle. This map has many things. Secrete rooms, buttons, and some other stuff. It also has many improvements. The S4S box is a more realistic texture, the fence is thicker, and the wall is less thick. So, have fun finding ALL the secretes!
